<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="grace-n">grace <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡreɪs/    美 /ɡreɪs/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1u">1.<strong>[U] 优美；优雅；[复数] 风度：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>add grace to what is already beautiful 
锦上添花</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She danced with much grace.
她舞姿婀娜。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He definitely lacked <strong>social graces</strong>.
他显然缺少社交风度。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>graceful /'ɡreɪsfl/ adj   </p></div>